			<div class="content">I decided to give this a go the other day, and I've had mixed results.<br /><br />My first attempt went really well, I charmed and hasted one mob, then managed to clear out one whole room of the shrine with him, before dispelling him and nuking him to death.  The next couple of attempts didn't go nearly as well, and after a few repeated charm breaks and having to gate out a couple of times I stopped for the night.  I gave it another shot tonight and died during the first fight when Charm broke (the mob my pet was fighting was at around 30% or so I believe).<br /><br />Here's a link to my Magelo, <a href="http://eq.magelo.com/profile/293462" class="postlink">Veravius</a><br /><br />My CHA is one point away from max (easily capped with CHA buff).  Obviously I need more Planar Power to increase the cap on that, but I'm working on getting two more AAs so I can buy Total Domination 3, which will hopefully help out a lot.  Other than that, I don't really know what the issue could be other than just plain bad luck.  That first run went really well, the pet worked out great and I raked in the XP, but since then I haven't had so much luck.</div>

			

